Instructions:

- Edit Datamodels in BIP server to specify correct data sources
- Edit Datamodels in BIP server to specify FTP server and FTP destination dir.
- Edit the Index template .rtf to specify the ftp directory in the hyperlink
- Load Hyperlinked_invoice_bursting.plb to BRM DB
- Other regular configuration for templates/reports mentioned in the docs

- and while running invoicing please run
	- pin_inv_accts -pay_type 10007
	- pin_inv_accts -pay_type 10001
	Note: Please do not run -hierarchy option which will do the stitching 
	and not the hyperlinking.
